document.full_text: northern europe is set to again bear the brunt of air traffic disruption from icelandic volcanic ash on wednesday after 500 flights were canceled on tuesday, but experts said the eruption was rapidly dying down.
document.title: ash to hit northern europe, but volcano dying down
